('c1059088-a64e-500e-be1f-07f1151e346c', 1, 'owner_age_proxy_rpls_tenure', 'positive', NULL, 'Senior RPLS HUGH WILLIAM CLARKSON (TBPELS license #4113) granted 1982-08-27 → 44yr tenure. TX RPLS requires 4yr college + 4yr supervised survey-in-training + state exam (typically earned at age 28-35); est. owner age ~74.', 'tbpels_rpls_roster', 'https://tbpedownloads.s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/rpls_roster.csv', '2026-05-16'),
('c1059088-a64e-500e-be1f-07f1151e346c', 2, 'firm_tenure_long', 'positive', NULL, 'Senior RPLS HUGH WILLIAM CLARKSON tenure 44yr per TBPELS RPLS roster. Firm registered as TBPELS Surveying Firm #10073800 since 2008-02-08. Passes >5yr settled-business hard gate.', 'tbpels_surveying_firms_roster', 'https://tbpedownloads.s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/sur-firm_roster.csv', '2026-05-16'),
('c1059088-a64e-500e-be1f-07f1151e346c', 2, 'rpls_license_skilled_trade_moat', 'positive', NULL, 'TX RPLS license = 4yr ABET-accredited surveying or equivalent + 4yr supervised survey-in-training + Tex. Occ. Code Ch. 1071 state exam. ~3,700 active RPLS statewide (TBPELS roster May 2026). Workforce documented as aging (TSPS workforce-shortage reports cite avg RPLS age >55).', 'tbpels_rpls_roster_aggregate', 'https://pels.texas.gov/roster/ls_rosters.html', '2026-05-16'),
('c1059088-a64e-500e-be1f-07f1151e346c', 4, 'low_pe_attention_vertical', 'positive', NULL, 'TX land surveying = LOW-PE-ATTENTION vertical. Only Bowman Consulting (NASDAQ:BWMN) + Westwood Professional Services (Endeavour Capital) are PE-backed rollup platforms active in TX surveying. Large-AEC strategics (Stantec/WSP/AECOM/Kimley-Horn/Cobb Fendley/LJA) only bolt-on $5M+ rev firms. Sub-$5M independent universe (Katy, Harris County) structurally under-targeted = opportunity zone. ETA/search-fund appetite emerging fast 2024-2026 per Stanford Search Fund Study (top-15 ETA vertical).', 'verticals.md skill config + Stanford Search Fund Study + Bowman 10-K filings', 'https://pels.texas.gov/roster/ls_rosters.html', '2026-05-16'),
